article:
This is a list of artists (bands and individual musicians) who recorded at least
one session for John Peel and his show on BBC Radio 1 from 1967 to his death in
2004. Details are taken from the
[http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio1/johnpeel/artists/ BBC Sessions listings], unless
otherwise noted. The first session was recorded by Tomorrow on 21
September 1967, and the last by Skimmer on 21 October 2004. Dates given below
are of recording rather than broadcast.

Where an artist has recorded more than one session under different names then
both names have been listed.
